Interface DataBucketADT<Value,​Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>>

Type Parameters:
Value - Elements that are going to share the same Key type key

All Known Implementing Classes:
GenericArrayListDataBucket
public interface DataBucketADT<Value,​Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>>
This abstract data type is an congregation of Value type elements which share a Key type key. Its mainly use is inside hash maps.
Author:
Borja Moralejo Tobajas
